title: Personal Portfolio for Remote Sensing
text:
Hi!
I am Yifei Lin frome Guangzhou, China.
Now I am a Master student from UCL, studying Urban Spatial Science in Centre for Advanced Spatial Analysis. I majored in Urban Planning at Sun Yat-sen University at undergraduate level, which is a five-year subject.
